sentences: Mark Schulman (born September 4, 1961 in Los Angeles, California) is an American musician and corporate speaker.
Schulman continues as P!nk's tour drummer and continues to be sought after by percussion and drummer's magazines in the U.S. and abroad; in 2013, he gave an interview for German magazine, Sticks.
Mark Schulman Interview NAMM Oral History Library (2020)
Schulman is currently on tour as a drummer with P!nk's band.
When Schulman is off from touring, Schulman gives drum clinics and gives presentations as a motivational speaker.
